10:["$","p","16",{"className":"article-p","children":["The unexpected finding wasn't the volume — it was the quality. QR-verified customers spend 23% more than walk-in customers, possibly because the recommendation from a trusted creator primes them to \"experience\" the meal rather than just eat it."]}]
